-- Czech President Klaus Refuses to Sign EU Rescue Fund, CTK Says
-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 2012-12-07T10:43:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-07/czech-president-klaus-refuses-to-sign-eu-rescue-fund-ctk-says.html
Czech President Vaclav Klaus won’t
sign an amendment to  Europe ’s Lisbon treaty that created the
European Stability Mechanism, he told the  CTK  new service.  Klaus’s refusal won’t block operations of the ESM rescue
fund, the state-run news service said, citing Vojtech Belling,
the director of the government’s European Affairs deparment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
